query:
INSERT INTO subscription (
                id,
                created_date_time,
                modification_date_time,
                client_id,
                client_name,
                program_id,
                object_operations
            )
            VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), now(), now(), $1, $2::text, $3, $4)
            RETURNING
                id,
                created_date_time,
                modification_date_time,
                client_name,
                program_id,
                object_operations
